 per site, $m>1$, making the presence of color very unlikely except\nmaybe for $m=2$ on the honeycomb lattice, for which the correction is only\nmarginally larger than the classical order parameter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Nov 2017 13:58:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-12"}
